
--------------
USING CRONTAB:
--------------
$ sudo crontab -e
Select nano and add this line:
@reboot python /home/pi/security/main.py --conf /home/pi/security/conf.json
@reboot sleep 35 && sudo python /home/pi/master.py &

========
