--------------------------------------------------------------------------
								EJECT??
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
You just need to do:

sudo apt-get install eject
sudo eject /dev/sda


Then udisks works just fine:

udisks --unmount /dev/sda
udisks --eject /dev/sda

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

cmd = "sudo umount /dev/sdb1"
os.system(cmd)

